*amaya-8.0 (28 Apr 2003)

  28 Apr 2003; Luca Barbato <lu_zero@gentoo.org> amaya-8.0.ebuild:
  New version.

30 Mar 2003; Luca Barbato <lu_zero@gentoo.org> amaya-7.2.ebuild:
  Enabled gtk support

*amaya-7.2 (22 Jan 2003)

  22 Jan 2003; Luca Barbato <lu_zero@gentoo.org> amaya-*.ebuild:
  New version, added IUSE

*amaya-7.1 (22 Jan 2003)

  22 Jan 2003; Luca Barbato <lu_zero@gentoo.org> amaya-*.ebuild:
  removed the 7.0 one since isn't present anymore, added the 7.1,
  added the "old" src uri just in case somebody wants the older 
  versions and the gentoo mirror is unreachable.

